<subSubSection pageId="22" pageNumber="23" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="22.[264,1323,964,1190]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[320,441,1084,1110]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Remarks.</emphasis>
The name of this taxon was originally given by 
<bibRefCitation author="Marseul, S. A. de" box="[1022,1205,1084,1110]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" pagination="171 - 218" refId="ref17243" refString="Marseul, S. A. de (1868) Description des especes nouvelles. L'Abeille, Memoires d'Entomologie, 5, 171 - 218." type="journal article" year="1868">Marseul (1868)</bibRefCitation>
as “viridi caerulans” and not “viridi coerulans”, thus the correct original spelling is 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Marseul" authorityYear="1868" box="[1136,1315,1124,1149]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridicaerulans">
<emphasis box="[1136,1315,1124,1149]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">viridicaerulans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, not 
<emphasis box="[309,488,1164,1189]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">viridicoerulans</emphasis>
as stated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Niehuis, M." box="[639,820,1164,1190]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" refId="ref17479" refString="Niehuis, M. (2004) Die Prachtkafer in Rheinland-Pfalz und im Saarland. Zugleich Beiheft 31 der Schriftenreihe &quot; Fauna und Flora in Rheinland-Pfalz &quot;. Landau, Gesellschaft fur Naturschutz und Ornithologie Rheinland-Pfalz e. V. (GNOR), 712 pp, figs." type="book" year="2004">Niehuis (2004)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
